{"tid":2478901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5理大生涉校園暴動　還押轉介區院受審","createTime":"2021-04-07T11:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T12:24:37.000Z","uid":283837,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b345c07247ab1287aa09ab0a7e18c9116d848bef","tid":2478901,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"反修例事件引發連續多月的示威衝突，其中在前年11月，大批示威者留守理工大學校園多日，與警方發生激烈衝突。其中有4男1女理大學生被指涉及有關衝突，現被控以暴動罪名。案件今天（7日）在九龍城法院再提訊，控方向法庭呈交轉介文件，申請將他們的案件轉介到區域法院審理。裁判官批准申請，下令將案件押後至4月27日，在區域法院提訊。期間5名被告要還押懲教署看管。<br />\n本案5名被告依次為林銘堯（22歲）、姜祖育（22歲）、姜紹熙（21歲）、陳蘊儀（女、23歲）及陳超卓（22歲）。首4名被告報稱學生，陳超卓則報稱文員，5人案發時均為理大學生。他們被控一項串謀暴動罪，控罪指他們於或約於2019年11月11至14日，在香港串謀與其他不知名人士於香港理工大學參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210407/bkn-20210407165904609-0407_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210407%2Fbkn-20210407165904609-0407_00822_001.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=20971265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210407/bkn-20210407165904609-0407_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d422ff77c97f7d6ddddb0d3b364d1b2510ba6923","tid":2478901,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50a3b52c78581322c5ad61d19177d8ec037d482","tid":2478901,"uid":122536,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"還柙師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4948d6e7b6af6da9cf1ac8b79e0e49190a1cb90","tid":2478901,"uid":291921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e191684184b8c98e7ff0092e2bfd9af70ca4d3a","tid":2478901,"uid":257125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /